  <name>SD Card Formatter (Unofficial Community Project)</name>
  <summary>Format SD cards with the official SD Card Formatter tool</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      A GTK3 graphical interface for Tuxera's official SD Card Formatter for Linux.
      This tool allows you to format SD cards properly according to SD specifications.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Simple and intuitive GTK3 interface</li>
      <li>Supports quick and full format options</li>
      <li>Automatic device detection</li>
      <li>First-run setup wizard for easy configuration</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Note: Due to licensing restrictions, the format_sd binary must be downloaded separately
      during first run. The application will guide you through this process.
    </p>
  </description>
  
